Comment: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:08.25,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Transcendam o espaço e o tempo
Comment: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:19.21,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Vindos de além do futuro, viajando pelo amanhã
Comment: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:21.98,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Habitem meus sonhos, habitem meu ser
Comment: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:33.75,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Se o relógio continuasse a ticar eternamente
Comment: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:39.89,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Quantos momentos únicos ele testemunharia?
Comment: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:45.45,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Destino! Com estas mãos, nós o agarramos
Comment: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.45,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Mesmo esta cidade selvagem
Comment: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:50.55,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Pode sentir os ventos da mudança
Comment: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:51.43,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,É agora!
Comment: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:53.65,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Timeranger, luz da esperança
Comment: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.14,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Vocês são como um raio que brilha
Comment: 0,0:00:57.18,0:01:02.75,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,E que se espalha sobre esta terra desolada
Comment: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:05.79,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Vindos de milhares de anos, além do futuro
Comment: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:08.46,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Transcendendo o tempo, viajando pelo amanhã
Comment: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:14.39,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Pessoas do futuro, vivam o "presente"
Comment: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:17.12,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Habitem meus sonhos, habitem meu ser
Comment: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:19.84,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Rumo a um amanhã mais radiante
Comment: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.68,OP-TR,,0,0,0,kara,Despertem!
